Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,成為宇宙公民的夢想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The dream of becoming a citizen of the cosmos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在2000年前 誕生於此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was born here, more than two millennia ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,亞歷山大城\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the city of Alexandria,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這座城市的名字是為了紀念它的征服者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}named after and conceived by its dead conqueror,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,已去世的亞歷山大大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alexander the Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,希臘的托勒密王朝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Ptolemys, the Greek kings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,繼承了亞歷山大帝國的埃及地區\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who inherited the Egyptian portion of Alexander's empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,並修建了這座圖書館\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}built this library
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,成立了相關的研究機構\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and its associated research institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可以說 這是非常罕見的舉措\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rarely, if ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不僅空前 而且絕後\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before or since,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,從沒有一個政府會花那麼多錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has there been a government that was willing to spend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把國家收入的大部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so much of its gross national product
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:00:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,投入到對知識的獲取中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the acquisition of knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有付出就有回報\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,知識的大時代來臨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,每一艘進入亞歷山大港的船隻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every ship entering Alexandria's harbor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都要進行搜查 查的不是違禁品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was searched-- not for contraband,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而是那些放在船上的書籍手抄本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but for books that might be copied and stored here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,發現後就歸入這座當時世界上最偉大的圖書館\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in what was then the greatest library on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,正是在這裏 圖書館的館長埃拉托斯特尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, Eratosthenes, one of the chief librarians,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,準確的計算出了地球的直徑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}accurately calculated the size of the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,並創建了地理學\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and invented geography.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,畢達哥拉斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pythagoras.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,希帕蒂婭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hypatia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,歐幾里得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Euclid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,歐幾里得在著作中闡述了幾何學的定律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Euclid set forth the precepts of geometry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,2300年後 他的著作依然被世人使用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in a textbook that remained in use for 2,300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,《聖經•舊約》也是從這裏開始散播到人世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Old Testament Bible comes down to us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,經書的大部分在這裏被翻譯成了希臘語\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}mainly from the Greek translations made here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很多偉大作品的原始手稿也保存在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The original manuscripts of the masterpieces
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,包括希臘的喜劇 戲劇 詩歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Greek comedy and drama, poetry,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,科學著作 工程著作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}science, engineering,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,醫學著作 歷史著作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}medicine and history--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,失落的古代文明作品被重新喚醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the total work product
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,妥妥的保存在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the awakening of ancient civilization-- were kept here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,據推測 這裏的藏書\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estimates vary on the total number of scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大概有50萬卷以上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They range from 500,000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至多達上百萬卷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to nearly a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的這些作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And all of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的這些書籍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只需要很小的一個空間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is but a tiny fraction of the information
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你的指尖那麼大的地方就可以保存了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you have at your fingertips at this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,人類集體的知識\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The collective knowledge of our species,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,存在我們自己的亞歷山大電子圖書館裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our own electronic Library of Alexandria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你身上帶有相應的設備 就隨時可以獲取\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}may be accessed by anyone who has a device
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你愛看什麼就看什麼 什麼時候想看就什麼時候看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the interest and the freedom to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可在過去的亞歷山大城 這樣的事情是不會發生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was not true in Alexandria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,知識只屬於某些精英人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where knowledge belonged to the elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因此在公元前四世紀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So in the fourth century AD,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,當暴民摧毀圖書館時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the mob came to destroy the library
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,當古典文明的精華被摧毀時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the genius of classical civilization,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有什麼人站起來保衛它們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there were not enough people to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等下一次的暴亂來臨時 又會發生些什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will happen the next time the mob comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,中文翻譯 幸福的微笑 timhal
